                  <h3 class="pb-2">Compare to microneedling rollers</h3>
                  <p class="text-justify p-2">
                    The needles in microneedling pens penetrate the skin vertically. Whereas with microneedling rollers, the needles
                    penetrate the skin at an angle, causing more chance of 'tears' through the skin leading to more side effects and longer
                    recovery time.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                  <img src="<%%= service.image2.url %>" alt="<%%= service.title %>">
                </div>
              </div>

