                    <%%= service.description2 %>
                  </p>
                </div>


                <div class="col-lg-6 pl-4">
                  <h3>Benefits of MTS</h3>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Needle is penetrated in epidermis</li>
                    <li>Promotes collagen regeneration</li>
                    <li>Improves skin tone</li>
                    <li>Reduces wrinkles and pigments</li>
                    <li>Activates skin cell restoration ability</li>
                    <li>Increases skin tightness & elasticity</li>
                    <li>Safe, convenient, economical</li>
                    <li>Non-surgial & Non invasive</li>
                    <li> No side effects</li>
                    <li>Easy to handle for treatment</li>
                    <li>No pain & No scratch</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

              </div>

